==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Coolly
<hw>Cool"ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a cool manner; without heat or
excessive cold; without passion or ardor; calmly; deliberately; with
indifference; impudently.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Coolness</ent>⟦br⟧
